2765862744.query: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM contributions WHERE (((tags @> '{"highway": "footway"}') OR (tags @> '{"highway": "path"}' AND (tags @> '{"foot": "designated"}' OR tags @> '{"foot": "yes"}')) OR (tags @> '{"highway": "pedestrian"}') OR (tags @> '{"highway": "steps"}') OR (tags @> '{"highway": "cycleway"}' AND tags @> '{"foot": "yes"}') OR (tags ? 'sidewalk' AND NOT tags @> '{"highway": "motorway"}') OR (tags @> '{"foot": "yes"}')) AND (status_geom_type).geom_type = 'LineString')

2696666561.query: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM contributions WHERE (status_geom_type).geom_type = 'LineString' AND (tags ? 'highway' OR tags @> '{"railway": "platform"}') AND NOT (tags @> '{"cycleway": "separate"}' OR tags @> '{"cycleway:both": "separate"}' OR (tags @> '{"cycleway:right": "separate"}' AND tags @> '{"cycleway:left": "separate"}') OR tags @> '{"indoor": "yes"}' OR tags @> '{"indoor": "corridor"}')
